If you were tuned in to the radio in the 90's, singer, songwriter, and producer,Â PaulaÂ Cole, has been woven into the fabric of your musical life with mega-hits such as "I Don't Want To Wait" and "Where Have All The Cowboys Gone?" Almost three decades on,Â PaulaÂ is still making great records and has recently released Lo, a collection of highly personal songs performed entirely live with her longtime collaborators, Jay Bellarose, Chris Bruce, Ross Gallagher, and Rich Hinman. Geoff Stanfield caught up withÂ PaulaÂ to chat about her new album, playing with Peter Gabriel, and more. Enjoy! Sponsored by: Soundtoys https://www.soundtoys.com/
